<p class="has-custom-charcoal-3-color has-text-color has-link-color has-custom-2-font-size" style="line-height:1.7">WordPress Campus Connect is a global educational initiative supported by the WordPress Foundation, a U.S.-based nonprofit organization that safeguards the free and open-source nature of WordPress. This program brings the power of WordPress to college campuses, helping students explore web technologies, digital tools, and open-source contribution through hands-on workshops led by experienced professionals from the WordPress community.<br><br>Whether you’re a student eager to learn, a college looking to empower your learners, or a WordPress contributor wanting to give back — Campus Connect is a platform where learning meets community.</p>
